{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_20","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/zsh -lc \"sed -n '1,460p' ui/app.slint\"","aggregated_output":"import { Theme, MediaItem, ContentRowData, UserInfo, PlayerState, SearchResult, ChapterInfo, MediaSegmentInfo } from \"theme.slint\";\nimport { HomeScreen } from \"home.slint\";\nimport { DetailScreen } from \"detail.slint\";\nimport { PlayerOverlay } from \"player.slint\";\nimport { LoginScreen } from \"login.slint\";\nimport { SearchScreen } from \"search.slint\";\nimport { LibraryScreen } from \"library.slint\";\nimport { SettingsScreen } from \"settings.slint\";\nimport { Screensaver } from \"screensaver.slint\";\nimport { LoadingSpinner } from \"loading.slint\";\nimport { ConfirmPopup } from \"popup.slint\";\nimport { LibraryTile, LibraryTilesRow } from \"library-tiles.slint\";\nimport { NowPlayingBar } from \"now-playing-bar.slint\";\nimport { CastMember, CastCrewRow, GenreTag, GenreRow } from \"cast-crew.slint\";\nimport { ChapterListPopup } from \"chapters.slint\";\nimport { TrickplayPreview } from \"trickplay.slint\";\nimport { PlaylistItem, PlaylistSidebar } from \"playlist.slint\";\nimport { MusicTrack, MusicPlayer } from \"music-player.slint\";\nimport { JellyfinBranding } from \"branding.slint\";\n\nexport global AppBridge {\n    // Navigation\n    callback navigate(/* screen */ string, /* param */ string);\n    callback go-back();\n\n    // Auth\n    callback login(/* user_id */ string, /* password */ string);\n    callback logout();\n\n    // Content loading\n    callback request-home-data();\n    callback request-library(/* library_id */ string, /* sort */ string, /* filter */ string);\n    callback request-item-detail(/* item_id */ string);\n    callback request-search(/* query */ string);\n    callback request-seasons(/* series_id */ string);\n    callback request-episodes(/* series_id */ string, /* season_id */ string);\n\n    // Playback\n    callback play-item(/* item_id */ string);\n    callback play-pause();\n    callback seek(/* position_ms */ int);\n    callback stop-playback();\n    callback next-track();\n    callback prev-track();\n    callback set-audio-track(/* index */ int);\n    callback set-subtitle-track(/* index */ int);\n    callback set-volume(/* level */ float);\n    callback toggle-mute();\n\n    // User actions\n    callback toggle-favorite(/* item_id */ string);\n    callback mark-played(/* item_id */ string);\n    callback mark-unplayed(/* item_id */ string);\n\n    // Library tiles\n    callback library-selected(string);\n\n    // Skip intro\n    callback skip-segment();\n\n    // Chapters\n    callback show-chapters();\n    callback seek-to-chapter(int);\n\n    // Speed control\n    callback speed-up();\n    callback speed-down();\n\n    // Subtitle delay\n    callback subtitle-delay-adjust(/* delta_ms */ int);\n\n    // Queue\n    callback queue-play-item(/* index */ int);\n    callback queue-remove-item(/* index */ int);\n    callback toggle-shuffle();\n    callback cycle-repeat();\n    callback enqueue-next(/* item_id */ string);\n\n    // Now playing bar\n    callback now-playing-clicked();\n\n    // Genre/cast\n    callback genre-selected(string);\n    callback person-selected(string);\n\n    // State properties (set by Rust)\n    in-out property <string> current-screen: \"login\";\n    in-out property <bool> is-loading: false;\n    in-out property <string> error-message: \"\";\n\n    // Data properties (populated by Rust)\n    in-out property <[UserInfo]> users: [];\n    in-out property <[ContentRowData]> home-rows: [];\n    in-out property <MediaItem> detail-item;\n    in-out property <[MediaItem]> detail-related: [];\n    in-out property <[MediaItem]> detail-seasons: [];\n    in-out property <[MediaItem]> detail-episodes: [];\n    in-out property <[MediaItem]> library-items: [];\n    in-out property <string> library-title: \"\";\n    in-out property <[SearchResult]> search-results: [];\n    in-out property <PlayerState> player-state;\n    in-out property <UserInfo> current-user;\n    in-out property <bool> show-screensaver: false;\n    in-out property <bool> show-popup: false;\n    in-out property <string> popup-title: \"\";\n    in-out property <string> popup-message: \"\";\n\n    // Library tiles\n    in property <[LibraryTile]> library-tiles;\n\n    // Now playing bar\n    in property <string> now-playing-title;\n    in property <string> now-playing-subtitle;\n    in property <image> now-playing-thumbnail;\n    in property <float> now-playing-progress;\n    in property <bool> now-playing-active;\n\n    // Cast & crew\n    in property <[CastMember]> cast-members;\n    in property <[GenreTag]> genres;\n\n    // Chapters\n    in property <[ChapterInfo]> chapters;\n\n    // Skip intro/credits\n    in property <bool> show-skip-button;\n    in property <string> skip-button-label;\n\n    // Playback speed\n    in property <string> speed-label: \"1.0x\";\n\n    // Playlist/queue\n    in property <[PlaylistItem]> queue-items;\n    in property <int> queue-current-index;\n    in property <bool> show-playlist;\n    in property <bool> shuffle-active;\n    in property <int> repeat-mode;\n\n    // Media player preference\n    in property <string> media-player: \"vlc\";\n    callback toggle-media-player();\n\n    // Trickplay\n    in property <image> trickplay-thumbnail;\n    in property <string> trickplay-timestamp;\n    in property <bool> trickplay-scrubbing;\n}\n\nexport component AppWindow inherits Window {\n    title: \"Jellyfin\";\n    background: Theme.background;\n    // Note: default-font-family and default-font-size set by system defaults\n    width: 1920px;\n    height: 1080px;\n\n    // Global key handler\n    FocusScope {\n        width: 100%;\n        height: 100%;\n\n        key-pressed(event) => {\n            if (event.text == Key.Escape) {\n                AppBridge.go-back();\n                return accept;\n            }\n            // Home key navigates to home screen\n            if (event.text == Key.F1) {\n                AppBridge.navigate(\"home\", \"\");\n                return accept;\n            }\n            return reject;\n        }\n\n        // Screen layers - only one visible at a time based on current-screen\n\n        if AppBridge.current-screen == \"login\" : LoginScreen {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            users: AppBridge.users;\n            select-user(id) => {\n                AppBridge.login(id, \"\");\n            }\n            submit-password(user-id, password) => {\n                AppBridge.login(user-id, password);\n            }\n        }\n\n        if AppBridge.current-screen == \"home\" : HomeScreen {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            rows: AppBridge.home-rows;\n            current-user: AppBridge.current-user;\n            item-selected(id) => {\n                AppBridge.navigate(\"detail\", id);\n            }\n            item-play(id) => {\n                AppBridge.play-item(id);\n            }\n            open-search() => {\n                AppBridge.navigate(\"search\", \"\");\n            }\n            open-settings() => {\n                AppBridge.navigate(\"settings\", \"\");\n            }\n            open-library(id) => {\n                AppBridge.navigate(\"library\", id);\n            }\n        }\n\n        if AppBridge.current-screen == \"detail\" : DetailScreen {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            item: AppBridge.detail-item;\n            related-items: AppBridge.detail-related;\n            seasons: AppBridge.detail-seasons;\n            episodes: AppBridge.detail-episodes;\n            genres: AppBridge.genres;\n            cast-members: AppBridge.cast-members;\n            play-item(item-id) => {\n                AppBridge.play-item(item-id);\n            }\n            navigate(screen, param) => {\n                AppBridge.navigate(screen, param);\n            }\n            toggle-favorite(item-id) => {\n                AppBridge.toggle-favorite(item-id);\n            }\n            mark-played(item-id) => {\n                AppBridge.mark-played(item-id);\n            }\n            mark-unplayed(item-id) => {\n                AppBridge.mark-unplayed(item-id);\n            }\n            request-seasons(series-id) => {\n                AppBridge.request-seasons(series-id);\n            }\n            request-episodes(series-id, season-id) => {\n                AppBridge.request-episodes(series-id, season-id);\n            }\n            genre-selected(name) => {\n                AppBridge.genre-selected(name);\n            }\n            person-selected(id) => {\n                AppBridge.person-selected(id);\n            }\n        }\n\n        if AppBridge.current-screen == \"search\" : SearchScreen {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            results: AppBridge.search-results;\n            search(query) => {\n                AppBridge.request-search(query);\n            }\n            select-result(id) => {\n                AppBridge.navigate(\"detail\", id);\n            }\n            go-back() => {\n                AppBridge.go-back();\n            }\n        }\n\n        if AppBridge.current-screen == \"library\" : LibraryScreen {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            items: AppBridge.library-items;\n            title: AppBridge.library-title;\n            item-selected(id) => {\n                AppBridge.navigate(\"detail\", id);\n            }\n            sort-changed(sort) => {\n                AppBridge.request-library(\"\", sort, \"\");\n            }\n            filter-changed(filter) => {\n                AppBridge.request-library(\"\", \"\", filter);\n            }\n            go-back() => {\n                AppBridge.go-back();\n            }\n        }\n\n        if AppBridge.current-screen == \"settings\" : SettingsScreen {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            username: AppBridge.current-user.name;\n            media-player: AppBridge.media-player;\n            logout() => {\n                AppBridge.logout();\n            }\n            toggle-media-player() => {\n                AppBridge.toggle-media-player();\n            }\n            go-back() => {\n                AppBridge.go-back();\n            }\n        }\n\n        // Player overlay - sits on top of content screens when playing\n        if AppBridge.current-screen == \"player\" : PlayerOverlay {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            state: AppBridge.player-state;\n            play-pause() => {\n                AppBridge.play-pause();\n            }\n            seek(position-ms) => {\n                AppBridge.seek(position-ms);\n            }\n            seek-relative(offset-ms) => {\n                AppBridge.seek(AppBridge.player-state.position-ms + offset-ms);\n            }\n            next-track() => {\n                AppBridge.next-track();\n            }\n            prev-track() => {\n                AppBridge.prev-track();\n            }\n            set-audio(index) => {\n                AppBridge.set-audio-track(index);\n            }\n            set-subtitle(index) => {\n                AppBridge.set-subtitle-track(index);\n            }\n            set-volume(level) => {\n                AppBridge.set-volume(level);\n            }\n            toggle-mute() => {\n                AppBridge.toggle-mute();\n            }\n            dismiss() => {\n                AppBridge.stop-playback();\n            }\n        }\n\n        // Now playing bar - visible when media is playing and not on the player screen\n        if AppBridge.now-playing-active && AppBridge.current-screen != \"player\" : NowPlayingBar {\n            width: 100%;\n            y: parent.height - self.height;\n            title: AppBridge.now-playing-title;\n            subtitle: AppBridge.now-playing-subtitle;\n            thumbnail: AppBridge.now-playing-thumbnail;\n            progress: AppBridge.now-playing-progress;\n            bar-visible: true;\n            bar-clicked() => {\n                AppBridge.now-playing-clicked();\n            }\n        }\n\n        // Loading overlay - visible on top of all screens when loading\n        if AppBridge.is-loading : Rectangle {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: Theme.background.with-alpha(0.7);\n\n            LoadingSpinner {\n                width: 80px;\n                height: 80px;\n                x: (parent.width - self.width) / 2;\n                y: (parent.height - self.height) / 2;\n                active: true;\n            }\n\n            // Escape must ALWAYS work, even during loading\n            FocusScope {\n                width: 100%;\n                height: 100%;\n                key-pressed(event) => {\n                    if (event.text == Key.Escape) {\n                        AppBridge.is-loading = false;\n                        AppBridge.go-back();\n                        return accept;\n                    }\n                    return reject;\n                }\n            }\n        }\n\n        // Error message overlay\n        if AppBridge.error-message != \"\" : Rectangle {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: Theme.background.with-alpha(0.85);\n\n            Rectangle {\n                width: 600px;\n                height: 200px;\n                x: (parent.width - self.width) / 2;\n                y: (parent.height - self.height) / 2;\n                background: Theme.surface;\n                border-radius: 12px;\n                border-width: 1px;\n                border-color: Theme.error;\n\n                VerticalLayout {\n                    alignment: center;\n                    padding: 32px;\n                    spacing: 16px;\n\n                    Text {\n                        text: \"Error\";\n                        color: Theme.error;\n                        font-size: 24px;\n                        font-weight: 700;\n                        horizontal-alignment: center;\n                    }\n\n                    Text {\n                        text: AppBridge.error-message;\n                        color: Theme.on-surface;\n                        font-size: 16px;\n                        horizontal-alignment: center;\n                        wrap: word-wrap;\n                    }\n\n                    Text {\n                        text: \"Press Escape to dismiss\";\n                        color: Theme.text-secondary;\n                        font-size: 14px;\n                        horizontal-alignment: center;\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n        }\n\n        // Confirm popup overlay\n        if AppBridge.show-popup : ConfirmPopup {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            visible-popup: true;\n            title: AppBridge.popup-title;\n            message: AppBridge.popup-message;\n            confirm() => {\n                AppBridge.show-popup = false;\n            }\n            cancel() => {\n                AppBridge.show-popup = false;\n            }\n        }\n\n        // Screensaver - topmost layer\n        if AppBridge.show-screensaver : Screensaver {\n            active: true;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            dismiss() => {\n                AppBridge.show-screensaver = false;\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_21","type":"reasoning","text":"**Investigating button functionality**\n\nI’m exploring the issue with the A button and why it doesn't perform any actions on the home screen. It seems like I might need to check the key handlers in HomeScreen, particularly focusing on if it’s expecting the space key instead. I should look into the specific key-pressed events in home.slint to troubleshoot further. There’s a need to delve deeper into the full implementation and see if it interacts properly across the FocusScope."}}
